#: ../../installation.rst:2
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../installation.rst:4
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer can be installed using pip, the Python package manager."
msgstr "CodeVideoRenderer 可以使用 Python 包管理器 pip 进行安装。"

#: ../../installation.rst:7
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前置条件"

#: ../../installation.rst:9
msgid "Before installing CodeVideoRenderer, ensure you have the following:"
msgstr "在安装 CodeVideoRenderer 之前，请确保您已具备以下条件："

#: ../../installation.rst:11
msgid "**Python 3.8 or higher**"
msgstr "**Python 3.8 或更高版本**"

#: ../../installation.rst:12
msgid "**pip** (Python package installer)"
msgstr "**pip**\\ （Python 包安装器）"

#: ../../installation.rst:13
msgid "**FFmpeg** (for video rendering)"
msgstr "**FFmpeg**\\ （用于视频渲染）"

#: ../../installation.rst:15
msgid ""
"We strongly recommend installing inside a virtual environment because Manim "
"(a heavy dependency) may conflict with other packages in your global Python "
"environment."
msgstr "我们强烈建议在虚拟环境中安装，因为 Manim（一个重量级依赖项）可能会与全局 Python 环境中的其他包发生冲突。"

