msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../installation.rst:47
msgid "Verifying FFmpeg"
msgstr "验证 FFmpeg"

#: ../../installation.rst:49
msgid "After installation, confirm FFmpeg is available in your ``PATH``:"
msgstr "安装完成后，请确认 FFmpeg 在您的 ``PATH`` 中可用："

#: ../../installation.rst:55
msgid ""
"You should see version information printed. If you get a \"command not "
"found\" error, restart your terminal or add FFmpeg to your system ``PATH`` "
"before continuing."
msgstr ""
"您应该能看到打印的版本信息。如果出现 \"command not found\" 错误，请重启终端或将 FFmpeg 添加到系统 ``PATH`` "
"后再继续。"

